① When baby is crying or can’t sleep well, do not hug them in your arms, or placed them in the cradle and kept shaking and shaking , causing immature baby’s brain and skull a hard collided , small blood vessels rupture, intracranial hemorrhage , resulting in  shaken baby syndrome ; 
② Do not accompany sleeping with long time, it will make the baby become  Oedipus  mentality, and under the accompany process ,if you hug your baby to sleep , you may suppress them ; 
③ Baby enjoys tummy sleeping , baby following five months can not turn over , it will not take the initiative to avoid obstacles in front of the mouth and nose , mouth and nose congestion and hypoxia tends to suffocate , so baby backs is the safest, which helps the respiratory tract unobstructed . For baby who just finished drinking milk , taken the right place to sleep , it will not choke if spits into the trachea. If you find your baby sleeping on their stomach , help the baby to timely adjust posture, to prevent accidents. 
④ With nipple sleep , it will suck the nipple when feeding after the baby woke up , so easy to make the baby’s gastrointestinal disorders and dyspepsia occurred ; Furthermore , shortness of breath, leading to disturbed sleep , and may even cause suffocation ; Moreover, it will affect the normal development of the baby’s gums , prone to tooth decay
